  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> tomatoes</strong> finely</p>\n<p>Trim, then slice the<strong> spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Cut the<strong> red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic </strong></p>",
